title: My smurf account is not synching with the boards
body: My smurf, TheVoidsPredator is not properly synching to the boards after leveling it up to five, it is also not allowing me to post on the Help & Support boards on that smurf account.

replies.body: I hit a button from our end that may have resolved the issue you're having with your smurf account. Go ahead and try making another post from that account and let me know if it worked. :)
It works, Thank you very much Targons Blade!
